name: Youngr - Flesh & Bones Live From Llamaland Studios

metadata.name: Youngr - Flesh & Bones (Live From Llamaland Studios)
metadata.description:
The 7th drop from the web3 album! 

This one's called Flesh & Bones and is basically about how music runs through my veins!!

Again, if you collect one of these badboys and head over to my tellie site- www.tell.ie/youngr - connect your wallet and discover loads of goodies behind the Token Gate. Stems / Demos / Artwork etc. 

As always... Love to Glass.xyz and love to all the collectors and the co-creators. 

Peace, love and music. 

Youngr. xxx
